/// Process-start handler registration is owned by `beskid_host` (`beskid_host_register_all` at link time; ABI v4 host/runtime split).
/// `RegisterHandlers()` remains a stable exported no-op for callers that still expect the v3 `Runtime.Init` hook symbol (tests, generated stubs, older docs).

pub i64 RegisterHandlers() {
    return 0;
}
